a. Planned Functionalities:

Creation of customers, articles, and sales invoices.
Establishing relationships between sales invoices, customers, and articles.
Retrieval of customer information, article information, and sales invoices.
b. Realized Functionalities:

Creation of customers, articles, and sales invoices.
Establishment of relationships between sales invoices, customers, and articles.
Retrieval of customer information, article information, and sales invoices.
c. Ideas for the Future:

Adding additional features like updating and deleting customer, article, and sales invoice records.
Implementing search and filtering capabilities for customer, article, and sales invoice data.
Enhancing user interface and user experience.
Implementing authentication and authorization for secure access to the application.
Generating reports and analytics based on sales data.